00:10:38.950 --> 00:10:40.690
My mother from Puerto Rico.

00:10:40.690 --> 00:10:43.460
My household, we were not
raised speaking Spanish,

00:10:43.460 --> 00:10:45.490
even though my parents
were Hispanic.

00:10:45.490 --> 00:10:47.790
They only spoke Spanish
to each other

00:10:47.790 --> 00:10:49.090
when they didn't want the children

00:10:49.090 --> 00:10:50.670
to know what they were
talking about [laughter].

00:10:50.670 --> 00:10:54.660
Okay. So, my first
language is English,

00:10:54.660 --> 00:10:57.700
but I look Hispanic, I think.

00:10:57.700 --> 00:11:00.760
Right? And my father
was in the Army.

00:11:00.760 --> 00:11:04.230
We were at a base, we were
living on a base in Texas.

00:11:04.230 --> 00:11:06.660
Although, at that point, when
this experience happened,

00:11:06.660 --> 00:11:07.960
