00:13:10.600 --> 00:13:12.850
No. So, anyways, what do you mean?

00:13:12.850 --> 00:13:14.150
So, I was labeled.

00:13:14.150 --> 00:13:15.640
I was discriminated against.

00:13:15.640 --> 00:13:18.580
I was also called gringa.

00:13:18.580 --> 00:13:21.170
Okay. That American girl, you know.

00:13:21.170 --> 00:13:22.500
So, I felt like an outsider.

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:24.700
It was a huge incentive
to learn Spanish.

